WEBVTT

00:00.801 --> 00:02.801
♪♪

00:02.870 --> 00:05.336
[croaking sound]

00:05.405 --> 00:06.170
I know.

00:06.239 --> 00:07.538
I can't believe it either.

00:07.607 --> 00:08.740
The map has never
called<i> me</i> before.

00:10.811 --> 00:13.412
I'm sure that's not why
she looks like that.

00:15.582 --> 00:16.848
Actually it is.

00:16.917 --> 00:18.817
Well, it's that and the fact
that you're being called

00:18.886 --> 00:20.052
to the royal palace!

00:20.121 --> 00:23.154
I mean, what in Equestria
could be going on there?

00:23.223 --> 00:25.457
Do you want me to come
with you? No. I shouldn't.

00:25.526 --> 00:28.293
The map just called you
for a reason, right?

00:28.362 --> 00:29.394
Though maybe it's a mistake.

00:29.463 --> 00:30.662
Not because of you!

00:30.731 --> 00:32.498
Because it's never called
just one of us before.

00:34.701 --> 00:38.269
I also wasn't nervous
before, but now...

00:38.338 --> 00:39.370
Don't worry.

00:39.439 --> 00:41.139
For all we know,
it's something small!

00:41.208 --> 00:42.307
Like maybe the cooks
are fighting over

00:42.376 --> 00:45.110
who has the best
butternut squash soup.

00:45.179 --> 00:47.812
Or the royal hairdressers
are fighting over a comb!

00:47.881 --> 00:49.414
Or ya know, maybe
the royal sisters

00:49.483 --> 00:51.282
aren't seeing eye-to-eye
on something.

00:51.351 --> 00:52.383
No!

00:52.452 --> 00:53.618
That's just crazy.

00:53.687 --> 00:57.122
Luna and Celestia
would never fight... again.

01:01.395 --> 01:04.662
So, the map sent you to
solve a friendship problem?

01:04.731 --> 01:06.531
Yes, Princess.

01:06.600 --> 01:08.166
Well, there's
nothing wrong here.

01:08.235 --> 01:09.667
Right, sister?

01:09.736 --> 01:12.837
No, everything's perfect
as usual, sister.

01:12.906 --> 01:16.341
♪♪

01:19.379 --> 01:22.680
<i>♪ My little pony,</i>
<i>my little pony ♪</i>

01:22.749 --> 01:24.616
<i>♪ Aaaahhh ♪</i>

01:24.685 --> 01:26.285
<i>♪ My little Pony ♪</i>

01:26.353 --> 01:29.254
<i>♪ I used to wonder what</i>
<i>friendship could be. ♪</i>

01:29.323 --> 01:31.023
<i>♪ My Little Pony ♪</i>

01:31.091 --> 01:33.591
<i>♪ Until you all shared</i>
<i>its magic with me. ♪</i>

01:33.660 --> 01:35.393
<i>♪ Big adventure! ♪</i>
<i>♪ Tons of fun ♪</i>

01:35.462 --> 01:37.228
<i>♪ A beautiful heart! ♪ ♪</i>
<i>Faithful and strong! ♪</i>

01:37.297 --> 01:39.731
<i>♪ Sharing kindness ♪</i>
<i>♪ it's an easy feat ♪</i>

01:39.800 --> 01:41.933
<i>♪ And magic makes it</i>
<i>all complete! ♪</i>

01:42.002 --> 01:44.235
<i>♪ To have my little pony ♪</i>

01:44.304 --> 01:47.739
<i>♪ Do you know you're all</i>
<i>my very best friends? ♪</i>

01:47.808 --> 01:49.875
♪♪

01:55.282 --> 01:59.317
♪♪

01:59.386 --> 02:00.652
Agh!

02:00.721 --> 02:02.821
Psst. Psst!

02:04.391 --> 02:07.559
♪♪

02:07.628 --> 02:10.295
Twilight? Is that you?

02:10.364 --> 02:11.896
How are you here?

02:11.965 --> 02:15.633
I'm not, I'm still home.
It's an easy spell.

02:15.702 --> 02:16.534
Anyway, enough
about me!

02:16.603 --> 02:17.435
I had to
check on you.

02:17.504 --> 02:18.469
Not in a
meddling way,

02:18.538 --> 02:20.405
in a friendly
how's-it-going way.

02:20.474 --> 02:21.739
Sooo, how's it going?

02:21.808 --> 02:23.808
Not great.

02:23.877 --> 02:27.378
I think the problem might be
between Celestia and Luna!

02:27.447 --> 02:29.347
Oh, no! That's terrible!

02:29.416 --> 02:30.648
I mean...

02:30.717 --> 02:32.717
What makes you say that?

02:32.786 --> 02:34.819
You know how someponies
say nothing's wrong

02:34.888 --> 02:38.223
but you can tell something's
definitely wrong?

02:38.292 --> 02:40.525
Noooo.

02:40.594 --> 02:42.393
That's basically what
the princesses did

02:42.462 --> 02:44.329
when I said there was
a friendship problem.

02:44.398 --> 02:46.698
Only they did it more,
you know, regally.

02:46.767 --> 02:48.800
I wish I could help
you, but I can't.

02:48.869 --> 02:51.502
Both for map reasons and
because I have no idea.

02:51.571 --> 02:52.570
This is big.

02:52.639 --> 02:53.639
Like really big.

02:55.575 --> 02:57.308
But I'm here if
you ever need to talk.

02:57.377 --> 02:57.976
Or listen to music!

02:58.045 --> 03:01.246
♪♪

03:01.315 --> 03:02.614
Comforting, right?

03:08.055 --> 03:10.488
Thank you so much for
breakfast, Princess!

03:10.557 --> 03:12.490
I can't believe you
cook it yourself!

03:12.559 --> 03:13.725
Of course, Starlight.

03:15.629 --> 03:17.762
I really enjoy doing it.

03:17.831 --> 03:20.431
It's a small way to
say "I care."

03:20.500 --> 03:21.500
[door opens suddenly]

03:23.403 --> 03:25.003
Good morning, sister!

03:25.072 --> 03:26.738
Join us?

03:26.807 --> 03:27.839
Too tired.

03:29.843 --> 03:30.876
Please excuse me.

03:33.547 --> 03:36.581
Wow. Last night must have
been really hard on her.

03:36.650 --> 03:40.385
Perhaps, but she is
like this every morning.

03:40.454 --> 03:46.391
♪♪

03:46.460 --> 03:50.028
So I think Luna may be hurting
her sister's feelings

03:50.097 --> 03:51.896
without even realizing it.

03:51.965 --> 03:53.264
Poor Celestia.

03:53.333 --> 03:55.033
That's so sweet that she makes
her sister pancakes

03:55.102 --> 03:56.734
every morning.

03:56.803 --> 03:58.002
She's your mentor.

03:58.071 --> 04:00.004
I think you might be biased.

04:00.073 --> 04:00.872
Fair enough.

04:00.941 --> 04:02.607
So what are you going to do?

04:02.676 --> 04:04.475
Nothing. Yet.

04:04.544 --> 04:05.977
I have to get all the facts.

04:06.045 --> 04:08.446
I asked Luna if I could spend
some time with her this evening.

04:08.515 --> 04:09.481
[knock]

04:09.549 --> 04:11.450
Princess Luna is waiting
for you, Miss.

04:12.686 --> 04:14.353
[nervous giggle]

04:16.089 --> 04:17.355
Good luck, Starlight!

04:17.424 --> 04:18.290
[whinny]

04:19.459 --> 04:20.391
[door closes]

04:20.460 --> 04:22.827
♪♪

04:22.896 --> 04:24.028
Wow, Princess Luna.

04:24.097 --> 04:25.863
You do this every night?

04:25.932 --> 04:28.499
Lavender's calming scent
is known to aid dreamers

04:28.568 --> 04:30.402
in achieving a
restorative sleep.

04:31.872 --> 04:33.738
That's so thoughtful!

04:33.807 --> 04:35.973
I try my best to make sure the
ponies in this castle

04:36.042 --> 04:37.975
sleep peacefully.

04:38.044 --> 04:40.778
(old woman voice)
So then I said, "touring?

04:40.847 --> 04:42.480
More like boring!"

04:42.549 --> 04:44.549
Ha ha hah!

04:44.618 --> 04:46.651
You really are a card!

04:46.720 --> 04:47.719
[polite laughter]

04:47.788 --> 04:48.887
[sigh]

04:48.956 --> 04:52.657
But as always, my sister's
too busy having fun

04:52.726 --> 04:55.660
with dignitary ponies to
acknowledge anything I do.

04:55.729 --> 04:56.862
Humph!

05:00.901 --> 05:04.435
So both princesses are hurting
each other without realizing it

05:04.504 --> 05:05.970
and instead of talking about it,

05:06.039 --> 05:08.573
they're just getting
colder and more distant.

05:08.642 --> 05:09.841
And they're Celestia and Luna,

05:09.910 --> 05:12.043
so it's not like you
can just confront them.

05:12.112 --> 05:14.045
Actually, that's exactly
what I was going to do.

05:14.114 --> 05:15.079
What?

05:15.148 --> 05:16.581
Are you crazy?

05:18.084 --> 05:20.718
I mean, you do whatever
you think is best.

05:20.787 --> 05:22.553
This is your mission.

05:22.622 --> 05:25.523
Gee, thanks for believing
in me, Twilight.

05:25.592 --> 05:26.691
I do!

05:26.760 --> 05:28.760
But... the last time the
princesses fought,

05:28.829 --> 05:31.529
Luna turned into Nightmare Moon
and Princess Celestia

05:31.598 --> 05:33.698
had to banish her for
a thousand years!

05:33.767 --> 05:35.733
That can't happen again.

05:35.802 --> 05:37.068
Well, I can't do nothing!

05:37.137 --> 05:39.003
The princesses aren't the
best at communicating

05:39.072 --> 05:39.904
with each other.

05:39.973 --> 05:40.938
[gasp]

05:41.007 --> 05:41.939
Sorry.

05:42.008 --> 05:43.174
It's just you
said "princesses"

05:43.243 --> 05:45.676
and "aren't the the best"
in the same sentence

05:45.745 --> 05:47.145
and it's making me nervous.

05:47.214 --> 05:48.613
[clunk]

05:48.682 --> 05:49.981
I'm not much help, am I?

05:50.050 --> 05:51.049
No!

05:53.220 --> 05:55.887
Wow, I almost feel
bad eating this.

05:55.956 --> 05:57.155
It's adorable!

05:57.224 --> 05:59.624
Like I said, I
enjoy this part.

06:04.798 --> 06:05.763
Hi.

06:05.832 --> 06:06.732
Princess Luna! Wait.

06:11.671 --> 06:14.806
As you both know, the map
sent me here for a reason

06:14.875 --> 06:18.876
and I think I've
found out what it is.

06:18.945 --> 06:22.713
Really? Oh, that is
wonderful, Starlight.

06:22.782 --> 06:23.915
What is it?

06:23.984 --> 06:25.716
You two.

06:25.785 --> 06:27.752
I beg your pardon?
- Excuse me?

06:27.821 --> 06:31.522
I think you're accidentally
hurting each other's feelings

06:31.591 --> 06:32.958
without realizing it.

06:35.195 --> 06:38.529
Princess Celestia, does it
bother you that Luna never

06:38.598 --> 06:42.133
notices the wonderful breakfasts
that you prepare for her?

06:42.202 --> 06:46.804
Yes. It does.

06:46.873 --> 06:50.641
Princess Luna, tell Celestia how
you feel about the fact

06:50.710 --> 06:52.210
that she never
acknowledges the work

06:52.279 --> 06:53.778
you put into
lining the hallway

06:53.847 --> 06:55.246
with lavender every night.

06:55.315 --> 07:00.551
I...Well, it's not
the best feeling.

07:00.620 --> 07:05.056
I'm sorry I never noticed you
make fruit faces on pancakes.

07:05.125 --> 07:06.424
But nights are long for me!

07:06.493 --> 07:09.594
You might be a morning
pony, but I am half asleep!

07:09.663 --> 07:11.662
You think I don't get tired?

07:11.731 --> 07:13.631
I'm exhausted.

07:13.700 --> 07:16.868
Oh, I apologize for not noticing
flowers in a wall sconce,

07:16.937 --> 07:19.070
but by the time I get
to retire for the night,

07:19.139 --> 07:20.771
I can barely see straight.

07:20.840 --> 07:24.109
Even so, I still make
an effort to smile.

07:25.345 --> 07:27.812
Like smiling is so hard!

07:27.881 --> 07:30.781
I'm sure that's not what
Princess Luna meant to say.

07:30.850 --> 07:32.617
Is that what "exhausts" you?

07:32.686 --> 07:35.219
Smiling and being
adored by everypony?

07:35.288 --> 07:37.755
And you have it so
much worse, do you?

07:37.824 --> 07:39.557
You spend your evenings
flitting around

07:39.626 --> 07:41.592
giving ponies
lovely dreams!

07:41.661 --> 07:43.027
Oh, it sounds just awful.

07:43.096 --> 07:45.162
OK.

07:45.231 --> 07:48.566
I feel like we should step
back, take a deep breath...

07:48.635 --> 07:51.802
Don't presume to know what it is
like to govern the dream realm!

07:51.871 --> 07:54.739
And yet you know exactly
what it's like to be me?

07:54.808 --> 07:56.173
Oh, please.

07:56.242 --> 07:57.174
Enough!

07:57.243 --> 07:58.910
[zap]

08:02.983 --> 08:04.382
There!

08:04.451 --> 08:09.020
Now you'll know exactly what
it's like to be each other!

08:09.089 --> 08:10.055
[gulp]

08:14.995 --> 08:17.161
What have you done?

08:17.230 --> 08:19.630
I went with my gut?

08:19.699 --> 08:21.866
Switch our cutie marks
back this instant.

08:21.935 --> 08:22.901
My apologies,
Your Majesties.

08:22.969 --> 08:26.003
But I can't, even
if I wanted to.

08:26.072 --> 08:28.105
This spell lasts
twenty-four hours.

08:28.174 --> 08:30.841
It may have been extreme, but...

08:30.910 --> 08:33.344
I think it's still a good idea.

08:33.413 --> 08:35.212
What?

08:35.281 --> 08:36.380
You said it yourselves.

08:36.449 --> 08:38.649
Neither of you believes
your sister knows

08:38.718 --> 08:40.618
how hard it is to be you.

08:40.687 --> 08:43.221
So this is your
chance to prove it.

08:45.291 --> 08:47.959
Well, I could use
an easy day

08:48.028 --> 08:49.827
followed by a good
night's sleep.

08:49.896 --> 08:51.162
You can try.

08:51.231 --> 08:54.231
I haven't had an easy
day in well, ever.

08:54.300 --> 08:58.035
But now, I get to sleep and
tonight will be a breeze.

08:58.104 --> 08:59.804
All right, Starlight Glimmer.

08:59.873 --> 09:01.205
We will do this.

09:01.274 --> 09:02.239
Good choice.

09:02.308 --> 09:03.240
Not that you had one.

09:03.309 --> 09:04.576
[nervous giggle]

09:05.779 --> 09:06.711
I'm gonna stop
talking now.

09:08.081 --> 09:10.381
[panting]

09:10.450 --> 09:12.750
You switched their cutie marks?

09:12.819 --> 09:15.853
The actual princesses'
cutie marks?

09:15.922 --> 09:18.656
I thought we
moved past this!

09:18.725 --> 09:21.025
It was the right
call... I hope.

09:21.094 --> 09:22.126
[gasping]

09:22.195 --> 09:23.227
[knock at door]

09:23.296 --> 09:24.762
Are you OK in there?

09:24.831 --> 09:25.730
I'm good!

09:25.799 --> 09:26.998
Just uh ...

09:27.067 --> 09:29.166
reading an exciting book.

09:29.235 --> 09:31.102
He's going to think I'm nuts.

09:31.171 --> 09:32.571
He's not the only one.

09:36.209 --> 09:39.777
As you can see, Celestia and
I are switching places today.

09:39.846 --> 09:43.280
Huh?

09:43.349 --> 09:45.950
I assure you, I am more than
capable of handling

09:46.019 --> 09:49.887
all of Celestia's
"duties." Dismissed!

09:49.956 --> 09:53.024
[grumbling]

09:53.093 --> 09:56.661
So what is first on my
dear sister's 'to do' list?

09:59.432 --> 10:02.299
It says you have a few
public appearances.

10:02.368 --> 10:04.935
Store openings, judging the
Royal Rose contest, you know,

10:05.004 --> 10:06.337
that sort of thing.

10:06.406 --> 10:08.939
Oh, I knew today would be easy

10:09.008 --> 10:11.108
but I didn't think it
would be that easy.

10:11.177 --> 10:15.847
♪♪

10:53.987 --> 10:57.088
"Princess Luna Unhappy
With Student Fund-raiser?"

10:57.157 --> 10:58.256
But I wasn't unhappy.

11:00.293 --> 11:03.027
Um, you are scowling.

11:03.096 --> 11:04.395
I didn't mean to.

11:04.464 --> 11:06.197
I'd been smiling all day.

11:06.266 --> 11:08.299
My cheeks hurt; I
stopped for one second

11:08.368 --> 11:10.768
and that's when he
took the picture!

11:10.837 --> 11:14.072
Guess smiling all day isn't
as easy as you thought?

11:16.810 --> 11:18.843
It says here that
because of me,

11:18.912 --> 11:21.946
the school didn't raise enough
funds to go on their field trip.

11:22.015 --> 11:23.915
I didn't mean for
that to happen!

11:25.185 --> 11:26.383
I know.

11:26.452 --> 11:28.352
But you can't dwell on that now.

11:28.421 --> 11:30.788
According to the list, some
delegates are about to arrive

11:30.857 --> 11:32.289
for a luncheon.

11:32.358 --> 11:34.291
You need to dispel
rumors of Timberwolves

11:34.360 --> 11:35.793
in the White Tail Woods.

11:35.861 --> 11:38.996
The nearby towns have been in
a state of panic for weeks.

11:39.065 --> 11:40.798
But I have to fix this.

11:40.867 --> 11:43.134
You can't.

11:43.203 --> 11:46.771
You need to put on a brave
face and help these ponies.

11:46.840 --> 11:48.973
It's what Celestia would do.

11:52.979 --> 11:54.845
HELLO! GREAT NEWS!

11:54.914 --> 11:56.715
THERE ARE NO TIMBERWOLVES!

11:58.251 --> 12:01.185
There are definitely
timberwolves!

12:01.254 --> 12:03.254
I'm sorry, but I
couldn't stop thinking

12:03.323 --> 12:05.556
about those poor students!

12:05.625 --> 12:08.125
Normally, I have all the time
and solitude I need

12:08.194 --> 12:10.361
to work through my
problems at my own pace.

12:10.430 --> 12:13.564
Well, your sister
doesn't get that luxury.

12:13.633 --> 12:17.802
[arguing]

12:17.871 --> 12:18.903
Ready for the
town hall?

12:18.972 --> 12:21.973
[shouting]

12:26.312 --> 12:27.211
Glad that's settled.

12:27.280 --> 12:29.246
That only took
three hours.

12:29.315 --> 12:30.948
That got heated
didn't it?

12:31.017 --> 12:31.916
Still on for
golf?

12:31.985 --> 12:33.484
Oh, absolutely!

12:33.553 --> 12:35.352
You made it to the
end of the day!

12:35.421 --> 12:36.620
Yay?

12:36.689 --> 12:42.159
Hmm? Oh, yes I'm just
going to turn in then.

12:42.228 --> 12:43.995
Goodlight, Starnight.

12:45.665 --> 12:47.932
Oh, hello, Starlight!

12:48.001 --> 12:51.335
I don't know about you, but
I feel very well-rested!

12:51.404 --> 12:53.204
Where's Luna?

12:53.273 --> 12:55.406
She already turned
in for the night.

12:55.475 --> 12:57.508
Did she now?

12:57.577 --> 13:00.979
It seems my duties were harder
than my sister expected.

13:06.152 --> 13:07.518
Moon raised.

13:07.587 --> 13:09.887
It's even easier
than raising the sun!

13:09.956 --> 13:11.222
What's next?

13:11.291 --> 13:13.891
[heavy breathing]

13:13.960 --> 13:15.159
Of course.

13:15.228 --> 13:17.161
Everypony's asleep at night.

13:17.230 --> 13:19.230
Luna works alone.

13:19.299 --> 13:21.532
Oh, but it's nothing
I can't handle!

13:21.601 --> 13:23.868
All I have to do is
watch over Equestria,

13:23.937 --> 13:25.603
visit the dream realm
and protect ponies

13:25.672 --> 13:27.504
in their nightmares.

13:27.573 --> 13:29.874
My list was three
times as long!

13:32.111 --> 13:33.110
All right.

13:33.179 --> 13:35.045
Everypony's asleep.

13:35.114 --> 13:37.448
You're talking to
yourself, Celestia.

13:37.517 --> 13:39.216
But there's nopony
else to talk to!

13:39.285 --> 13:40.517
Yet.

13:40.586 --> 13:42.587
I can talk to ponies
in their dreams!

13:50.997 --> 13:53.564
Now to save some ponies
from their nightmares,

13:53.633 --> 13:56.033
which aren't real so it
shouldn't be too hard, right?

13:56.102 --> 13:58.436
Right. Good call, Celestia!

14:00.073 --> 14:01.972
And I'm talking to myself again.

14:02.041 --> 14:03.208
[scream]

14:04.577 --> 14:05.443
I care.

14:05.645 --> 14:06.443
I care.

14:06.512 --> 14:07.378
I care.

14:07.580 --> 14:08.580
I Care.

14:08.782 --> 14:09.981
[scream]

14:13.152 --> 14:14.018
No!

14:15.321 --> 14:16.387
This is big!

14:16.456 --> 14:17.521
Like really big!

14:17.590 --> 14:18.989
Wah!

14:19.058 --> 14:20.925
Starlight, I'm here now.

14:20.994 --> 14:22.526
Tell me what's wrong.

14:22.595 --> 14:25.229
Going with my gut
was the wrong call!

14:25.298 --> 14:27.431
I was supposed to bring
you two closer together,

14:27.500 --> 14:29.533
but I've only driven you apart!

14:29.602 --> 14:31.669
If you two can't see why
you need each other, then...

14:31.738 --> 14:33.438
Then I am back!

14:35.508 --> 14:38.442
[nasty laugh]

14:38.511 --> 14:39.978
Don't worry, Starlight.

14:42.015 --> 14:44.248
I know how to handle
Nightmare Moon.

14:44.317 --> 14:49.320
Yes, but can you handle me?

14:49.389 --> 14:53.892
[nasty laugh]

14:56.629 --> 15:00.431
[screeching laugh]

15:00.500 --> 15:02.066
This can't be!

15:02.135 --> 15:04.535
If Luna can turn
into Nightmare Moon,

15:04.604 --> 15:08.572
you can absolutely turn
into me, Daybreaker.

15:08.641 --> 15:12.476
The better, prettier and
more powerful version of you.

15:12.545 --> 15:15.179
No. I'll never turn into you!

15:15.248 --> 15:17.614
Deep inside you know
how powerful you are.

15:17.683 --> 15:19.550
You don't need Luna.

15:21.421 --> 15:22.553
That's not true.

15:22.622 --> 15:25.456
Even when we were apart,
I knew I needed her.

15:25.525 --> 15:28.659
Oh, please!

15:28.728 --> 15:31.228
You don't need anypony.

15:31.297 --> 15:34.565
You can do whatever you want
and all you have to do

15:34.634 --> 15:38.002
is get rid of anypony
who stands in your way.

15:38.071 --> 15:42.039
[zap]

15:42.108 --> 15:44.241
I never should have
banished you to the moon.

15:44.310 --> 15:46.510
I should have destroyed you!

15:46.579 --> 15:48.312
No! You can't do that!

15:48.381 --> 15:52.282
Day, night, sun, moon -
Equestria needs both of you.

15:52.351 --> 15:54.385
Without balance,
there's no harmony!

15:57.657 --> 16:00.291
Who needs balance when
you can have it all?

16:03.463 --> 16:06.463
You can't get rid of
me so easily, sister.

16:06.532 --> 16:09.367
Unless you plan on
smiling me to smithereens.

16:10.703 --> 16:12.369
Enough!

16:12.438 --> 16:16.574
I told you I was more
powerful than you.

16:19.745 --> 16:21.678
Ugh. So much black.

16:21.747 --> 16:23.480
We get it, you're sad!

16:23.549 --> 16:26.350
You could really use some sun.

16:26.419 --> 16:29.420
♪♪

16:37.897 --> 16:39.496
This is all my fault!

16:39.565 --> 16:41.598
I never should have
gone on this mission.

16:41.667 --> 16:43.301
Now Equestria is doomed!

16:50.510 --> 16:53.477
<i>♪ That smile's too wide. ♪</i>

16:53.546 --> 16:56.680
<i>♪ It's obviously not real. ♪</i>

16:56.749 --> 16:59.751
<i>♪ [eerie music] ♪</i>

17:03.856 --> 17:07.791
Why don't you want us to go
on our field trip?

17:07.860 --> 17:09.060
I don't!

17:10.863 --> 17:15.199
I mean, I do!

17:15.268 --> 17:16.733
<i>♪ That smile's too wide. ♪</i>

17:16.802 --> 17:19.303
<i>♪ It's obviously not real. ♪</i>

17:19.372 --> 17:21.238
Celestia!

17:21.307 --> 17:22.473
I'm so glad you're...

17:30.650 --> 17:31.449
I've seen a lot,

17:31.518 --> 17:33.250
but I haven't seen this before.

17:33.319 --> 17:34.852
It's Starlight Glimmer's.

17:34.921 --> 17:37.788
She's afraid this is what would
happen if we continue to fight!

17:37.857 --> 17:39.256
[sobbing]

17:39.325 --> 17:40.357
What was I thinking?

17:40.426 --> 17:43.193
I'm never going
with my gut again!

17:43.262 --> 17:45.362
If you don't fix this soon, it
could have a grave consequence

17:45.431 --> 17:46.830
on Starlight's psyche.

17:46.899 --> 17:48.699
But my magic isn't
powerful enough.

17:48.768 --> 17:50.534
I thought if we
work together--

17:50.603 --> 17:52.436
I have your magic,
remember?

17:52.505 --> 17:53.804
It doesn't work in
the dream realm.

17:53.873 --> 17:55.506
It has to be you.

17:55.575 --> 17:57.841
Oh, Luna, I can't
do this!

17:57.910 --> 18:01.478
I was wrong. Your job
is so incredibly hard.

18:01.547 --> 18:03.347
You have to battle nightmares
and work in the darkness

18:03.416 --> 18:05.382
and do it all alone.

18:05.451 --> 18:08.819
It takes such a brave, strong
pony to do what you do!

18:08.888 --> 18:10.687
and that pony is you.

18:10.756 --> 18:11.955
I walked a day in your shoes.

18:12.024 --> 18:14.658
I thought all you had to do
was smile and be adored

18:14.727 --> 18:16.693
all the time, but I was wrong.

18:16.762 --> 18:18.795
There is so much
more to it than that.

18:18.864 --> 18:22.366
[shrieking laughter]

18:22.435 --> 18:24.535
[zap]

18:24.604 --> 18:25.536
[scream]

18:25.605 --> 18:26.603
[thud]

18:26.672 --> 18:28.672
♪♪

18:28.741 --> 18:32.577
[nasty laughter]

18:34.313 --> 18:35.780
Don't do this to each other!

18:38.651 --> 18:40.484
In order to defeat Daybreaker,

18:40.553 --> 18:44.288
you need only to trust in
your strength, as I do.

18:49.629 --> 18:51.695
You can't destroy me!

18:51.764 --> 18:55.199
I'm everything you want to be!

18:55.268 --> 18:57.367
No, you're not.

18:57.436 --> 19:01.438
You are not real and you
will never exist again!

19:01.507 --> 19:02.973
[whoosh]

19:03.042 --> 19:04.341
[shouts]

19:04.410 --> 19:05.409
[whomp]

19:08.347 --> 19:09.546
You did it!

19:09.615 --> 19:11.515
Only because you were here.

19:11.584 --> 19:14.218
I don't know how
you do this alone.

19:14.287 --> 19:15.019
So um...

19:15.088 --> 19:16.420
did you talk
to yourself?

19:16.489 --> 19:17.588
Um... a little.

19:17.657 --> 19:19.723
[giggling]

19:19.792 --> 19:21.225
Is this really happening?

19:21.294 --> 19:22.693
Or is this still a dream?

19:28.534 --> 19:30.267
Welcome back, sister!

19:30.336 --> 19:34.371
I know you had a long night
so I made you some pancakes.

19:34.440 --> 19:35.672
Oh!

19:35.741 --> 19:37.908
How... nice.

19:37.977 --> 19:38.910
Ahem.

19:40.479 --> 19:41.778
[gulp]

19:41.847 --> 19:44.281
They are delicious.

19:44.350 --> 19:45.549
Thank you.

19:45.618 --> 19:47.551
[laughter]

19:47.620 --> 19:51.321
I know that face;
they're not.

19:51.390 --> 19:53.624
I know you have to be
perfect for everypony else

19:53.693 --> 19:58.495
and you do an amazing job but
you don't have to do it for me.

19:58.564 --> 20:01.298
In that case...these
are terrible!

20:01.367 --> 20:02.766
[laughter]

20:02.835 --> 20:04.801
I know!

20:04.870 --> 20:07.471
But it means a lot
that you tried.

20:07.540 --> 20:08.739
I love you, sister.

20:08.808 --> 20:10.707
I love you too.

20:10.776 --> 20:13.644
So this was real!

20:13.713 --> 20:15.479
[yawn]

20:15.548 --> 20:18.682
Or was it not real and
this just happened now

20:18.751 --> 20:20.784
and not in my dream?

20:20.853 --> 20:22.552
I'm so confused.

20:22.621 --> 20:23.987
[laugh]

20:24.056 --> 20:26.290
It's all real.

20:26.359 --> 20:29.026
It was the right call,
going with your gut.

20:29.095 --> 20:31.561
The map was wise to
send you, Starlight.

20:31.630 --> 20:35.399
Nopony else would have been
so bold as to do what you did.

20:35.468 --> 20:38.368
That's a nice way of saying
I came dangerously close

20:38.437 --> 20:40.304
to messing everything up.

20:40.373 --> 20:42.306
It was just
what we needed.

20:42.375 --> 20:45.008
The experience has made
us closer than ever.

20:45.077 --> 20:49.579
[zap]

20:49.648 --> 20:50.714
Wait...

20:50.783 --> 20:51.948
I'm not doing this!

20:52.017 --> 20:55.919
♪♪

20:55.988 --> 20:59.356
I believe that one means
your mission is complete.

20:59.425 --> 21:01.425
Wow. I can't wait
to tell Twilight!

21:01.494 --> 21:02.392
[crash]

21:02.461 --> 21:03.593
I already know!

21:03.662 --> 21:04.728
I mean I don't know everything.

21:04.796 --> 21:07.097
I just got here to bring
you your toothbrush.

21:07.166 --> 21:08.365
So this is just
a friendly visit,

21:08.434 --> 21:09.833
not interfering because I
was worried! I wasn't.

21:09.902 --> 21:13.470
I knew you could do it and
I'm so so so so proud of you!

21:13.539 --> 21:15.038
Tell me everything. Start
from after I hyperventilated

21:15.107 --> 21:16.573
and don't leave
out any details!

21:16.642 --> 21:19.910
♪♪

21:19.979 --> 21:21.878
Oh, uh., by the way,
there's a field trip

21:21.947 --> 21:23.213
you need to make happen

21:23.282 --> 21:26.116
What?
- and a timberwolf issue
you need to address.

21:26.185 --> 21:28.418
Oh! Look there's the sun!
Time for me to turn in!

21:28.487 --> 21:31.489
♪♪
